com.identityx.clientSDK

Class SystemRepoFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.identityx.clientSDK.base.BaseRepoFactory
      • com.identityx.clientSDK.SystemRepoFactory

  • public class SystemRepoFactory
extends BaseRepoFactory
    Class used to get repositories related to the system. Once this class is created and initialised correctly, the repositories are provided configured and ready to use. In order to use the system repositories a system account is required, that means the token or the Active Directory credentials used for access need to have system level permissions.
